{"type":null,"faqId":21632,"title":"如何使用NFC连接手环？（For Android）","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-indent:0.008333334in;margin-left:0.29166666in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n</p>\n首先，您的手机必须要支持NFC功能。<br>\n操作方法：长按手环电源键开机，打开手机的NFC功能，将手机的NFC贴片靠近手环，这时候界面上会弹出蓝牙连接的提示，按照提示连接蓝牙即可。<br>\n<p>\n</p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":203,"faqType":"兼容与支持","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5333","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-System-Requirements-Support","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1427334705000,"seriesProductName":"B1-Honor","visitedTimes":287,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀手环,B1,NFC,","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}